# ---- Figures ----
# We do NOT block image extensions at the top level so that
# paper / README figures committed in subfolders (e.g. time-xl/figures/) pass
# through. Per-run figures are already covered by the runs/ / results/ /
# checkpoints/ rules above. Add specific entries below if you produce ad-hoc
# figures at the repo root that should not be committed.
#
# *.png
# *.jpg
# *.pdf

# ---- HPC / scheduler scripts (kept out of this public release) ----
*.slurm
**/slurm/

# ---- Local helper scripts you don't want to publish ----
sync_*.sh
sync_*.bat
reset_*.ps1

# ---- Misc local-only ----
data_local/
